This PR simply removes the scheme restriction from the Markdown and Emmet extension's language features. This allows these features to apply to virtual file systems (e.g. [GistPad](https://aka.ms/gistpad), in addition to just local files and untitled files. I tested all of these features in local files, non-file based files, as well as within a Live Share session, and everything works as expected 👍 

